title: Bedroom(s) Available for Lease Takeover In East Rock!
text:
- 1 Bedroom (pictured in post) available Dec. 19 - July 31, 2021 with option to extend on another lease.
- Second bedroom if desired available at the beginning of the semester! Perfect for a pair of friends or coworkers! Bedroom is located on top floor of beautiful East Rock home located on Cottage St. just doors down from East Rock Coffee. Den study space (pictured) is just outside both rooms. Bathroom w/shower is upstairs as well shared between two people.
Home is 5 bedroom, 2 bathroom. Ample...
